TextEng: "True. Me no want more stuff to worry 'bout."
"True. I really don't want to know."
"True. Me gots troubles. But me likes to hear yours anyways."
Text: "맞아. 나 문제 있어. 근데 나 네 얘기도 듣고 싶어."

TextEng: "True, I have troubles; but sometimes it helps to share them."
Text: "맞아요, 전 문제가 있어요. 하지만 때론 나누는 게 도움이 되죠."

TextEng: "That be it? Me listen to you for no reason?"
Text: "그게 다야? 나 아무 이유 없이 들은 거야?"

TextEng: "That's it? I listened to all that for no reason?"
Text: "그게 다예요? 제가 아무 이유 없이 다 들은 거예요?"
